        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Harmful Algal Bloom Essential Forecasting Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Harmful Algal Bloom Operational Forecast System to continue to operate during a government shutdown by designating certain activities related to the system as excepted services under the Anti-Deficiency Act.</p>]]>
        </text>
